\c 6
\s UJesu udelelwa ngabeNazaretha
\p
\v 1 Wasesuka lapho, waya emzini wakibo; abafundi bakhe basebemlandela.
\v 2 Sekufike isabatha, waqala ukufundisa esinagogeni; labanengi aba\add mu\add*zwayo bamangala, bathi: Zivela ngaphi lezizinto kuye? Njalo yinhlakanipho bani ayinikiweyo, ukuthi lalimisebenzi yamandla enje yenziwe ngezandla zakhe\x + Mat. 13.54-58.\x*?
\v 3 Lo kayisuye umbazi yini, indodana kaMariya, lomfowabo kaJakobe loJose loJudasi loSimoni\x + Mat. 13.55.\x*? Labodadewabo kabakho yini lapha kithi? Basebekhubeka ngaye.
\v 4 Kodwa uJesu wathi kubo: Umprofethi kasweli ukudunyiswa, ngaphandle kwelizweni lakibo, lezihlotsheni zakhe lendlini yakwabo.
\v 5 Futhi wayengelakho ukwenza lowodwa umsebenzi wamandla lapho\x + 9.23. Gen. 19.22.\x*, ngaphandle kokubeka izandla phezu kwabagulayo abalutshwana, wa\add ba\add*silisa\x + Luka 13.13.\x*.
\v 6 Wasemangala ngokungakholwa kwabo\x + Isa. 59.16.\x*. Wabhodabhoda imizana efundisa\x + Mat. 9.35. Luka 13.22.\x*.
\s Ukuthunywa kwabaphostoli
\p
\v 7 Wasebizela kuye abalitshumi lambili\x + Mat. 10.1.\x*, waqala ukubathuma ngababili ngababili\x + 6.39,40.\x*, wabanika amandla phezu kwabomoya abangcolileyo\x + Mat. 10.1.\x*.
\v 8 Wabalaya ukuthi bangaphathi lutho lwendlela, ngaphandle kodondolo kuphela; lasikhwama, lasinkwa, lamali\f + \fk imali: \ft ibala litsho ucezu lwemali yethusi, kodwa lapha kuthathwa njengemali nje\f* ezwezweni\x + Mat. 10.9-15. Luka 9.3-5; 10.4-12.\x*;
\v 9 kodwa bafake amanyathela\x + Seb. 12.8. Mat. 10.10. Luka 15.22.\x*; futhi bangembathi izembatho ezimbili.
\v 10 Wasesithi kubo: Lapho elingena khona endlini, hlalani kiyo lize liphume khona\x + Eks. 18.4.\x*.
\v 11 Njalo loba ngobani abangayikulemukela, kumbe balizwe, nxa liphuma lapho, thintithani uthuli olungaphansi kwenyawo zenu kube yibufakazi kubo\x + Mat. 8.4.\x*. Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Kuzakuba lula eSodoma kumbe laseGomora ngosuku lwesigwebo, kulakulowomuzi.
\v 12 Sebephumile batshumayela ukuthi baphenduke\x + Mat. 10.7. Luka 10.9.\x*;
\v 13 bakhupha amadimoni amanengi, bagcoba abanengi abagulayo ngamagcobo\x + Jak. 5.14.\x* ba\add ba\add*silisa\x + Mat. 10.7. Luka 10.9.\x*.
\s Ukubulawa kukaJohane uMbhabhathizi
\p
\v 14 Inkosi uHerodi\x + 6.22,26,27. Mat. 14.1.\x* wasesizwa \add ngakho\x + Mat. 14.1-12. Luka 9.7-9.\x*\add*, ngoba ibizo lakhe laba sobala, wasesithi: UJohane owabhabhathizayo uvukile kwabafileyo, futhi kungakho lamandla esebenza kuye.
\v 15 Abanye bathi: UnguElija; labanye bathi: Ungumprofethi, kumbe \add u\add*njengomunye wabaprofethi.
\v 16 Kodwa uHerodi esezwile wathi: Lo nguJohane, mina engamquma ikhanda; yena uvukile kwabafileyo\x + 8.28. Mat. 16.14.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Ngoba yena uHerodi wayethumele wambamba uJohane, wambopha entolongweni, ngenxa kaHerodiyasi umkaFiliphu umfowabo, ngoba wayemthethe\x + Luka 3.19,20.\x*.
\v 18 Ngoba uJohane wayethe kuHerodi: Kawuvunyelwa ukuba lomkamfowenu.
\v 19 UHerodiyasi wasembambela inhliziyo, wafuna ukumbulala; kodwa kenelisanga;
\v 20 ngoba uHerodi wayemesaba uJohane, esazi ukuthi uyindoda elungileyo lengcwele, wamlondoloza; lalapho emuzwa, wenza izinto ezinengi\x + Luka 2.19.\x*, wamuzwa ngokuthokoza\x + 12.37. Mat. 13.20.\x*.
\p
\v 21 Kwathi selufikile usuku oluhle, uHerodi ngelanga lakhe lokuzalwa wenzela izikhulu zakhe\x + 1 Kho. 3.15.\x* lenduna zenkulungwane\x + Isam. 6.15; 19.18.\x* labalisa\x + Luka 19.47. Seb. 13.50; 17.4; 25.2; 28.7,17.\x* beGalili\x + Luka 3.1.\x* ukudla kwantambama,
\v 22 kwathi indodakazi kaHerodiyasi lo isingenile yagida, yamkholisa uHerodi lalabo ababehlezi ekudleni laye, inkosi yathi entombini: Cela kimi loba kuyini okuthandayo, njalo ngizakupha;
\v 23 wafunga kuyo \add esithi\add*: Loba kuyini ongakucela kimi, ngizakunika\x + 6.22,26,27. Mat. 14.1.\x*, kuze kube yingxenye yombuso wami\x + Esta 5.3,6; 7.2.\x*.
\v 24 Yasiphuma isithi kunina: Ngizacelani? Yena wasesithi: Ikhanda likaJohane uMbhabhathizi.
\v 25 Njalo yahle yangena enkosini ngokuphangisa\x + Luka 1.39.\x*, yacela, yathi: Ngifuna ukuthi unginike khathesinje emganwini ikhanda likaJohane uMbhabhathizi.
\v 26 Inkosi yasidabuka kakhulu, \add kodwa\add* ngenxa yezifungo langalabo ababehlezi layo ekudleni\x + Mat. 13.21.\x* kayithandanga ukuyilandulela\x + 7.9.\x*.
\v 27 Njalo inkosi yahle yathuma ibutho yalaya ukuthi kulethwe ikhanda lakhe. Wasehamba wamquma ikhanda entolongweni,
\v 28 waletha ikhanda lakhe ngomganu, walinika intombi; intombi yasilinika unina.
\v 29 Kwathi abafundi bakhe sebezwile beza, bathatha isidumbu sakhe, basibeka engcwabeni\x + Mat. 24.28. Isam. 11.8,9.\x*.
\s UJesu usuthisa amadoda azinkulungwane ezinhlanu
\p
\v 30 Abaphostoli basebebuthana kuJesu\x + 6.30,31, Luka 9.10.\x*, bambikela konke, lababekwenzile kanye lababekufundisile.
\v 31 Wasesithi kubo: Wozani lina lodwa endaweni eyinkangala\x + Mat. 10.2. Luka 6.13; 17.5; 22.14; 24.10.\x*, liphumule kancinyane\x + 6.30,31, Luka 9.10.\x*. Ngoba babebanengi abafikayo labahambayo, futhi bengelathuba lokudla\x + 3.20.\x*.
\p
\v 32 Bakhuphuka ngomkhumbi\x + 3.9.\x* baya endaweni eyinkangala bebodwa\x + Mat. 14.13-21. Luka 9.10-17. Joha. 6.1-13.\x*.
\v 33 Amaxuku asebabona besuka, labanengi bamazi, bagijimela khona kanyekanye ngenyawo bevela emizini yonke, basebebandulela, bahlangana kuye.
\p
\v 34 Kwathi uJesu esephuma wabona ixuku elikhulu, waba lesihelo ngabo\x + Mat. 15.32-38. Mark. 8.2-9.\x*, ngoba babenjengezimvu ezingelamelusi\x + Mat. 9.36.\x*; waseqala ukubafundisa izinto ezinengi\x + Luka 9.11.\x*.
\p
\v 35 Kwathi isikhathi sesihambile, abafundi bakhe beza kuye bathi: Lindawo iyinkangala, lesikhathi sesihambile;
\v 36 bayekele, ukuze baye ezigabeni ezizingelezeleyo lemizaneni bazithengele izinkwa; ngoba bengelalutho abangaludla.
\v 37 Wasephendula wathi kubo: Banikeni lina ukuthi badle. Basebesithi kuye\x + Joha. 6.7.\x*: Sihambe yini siyethenga izinkwa \w ngabodenariyo\w** abangamakhulu amabili, sibaphe badle\x + Nani 11.13,21,22. 2 Kho. 4.43.\x*?
\v 38 Wasesithi kubo: Lilezinkwa ezingaki? Hambani liyebona. Sebesazi bathi: Zinhlanu, lenhlanzi ezimbili.
\v 39 Wasebalaya ukuthi babahlalise bonke phansi ngezigaba ngezigaba etshanini obuluhlaza\x + 6.7.\x*.
\v 40 Basebehlala phansi ngamaviyo ngamaviyo, ngamakhulu langamatshumi amahlanu\x + 6.7.\x*.
\v 41 Wasethatha izinkwa ezinhlanu lenhlanzi ezimbili, ekhangela phezulu ezulwini, wabonga, wazihlephula izinkwa, wa\add zi\add*nika abafundi bakhe ukuthi ba\add zi\add*beke phambi kwabo; lenhlanzi ezimbili wazabela bonke.
\v 42 Basebesidla bonke, basutha.
\v 43 Basebedobha izitsha ezilitshumi lambili ezagcwala imvuthu ezazisele, l\add okuseleyo\add* kwenhlanzi.
\v 44 Lalabo abadlayo izinkwa, babengaba ngamadoda azinkulungwane ezinhlanu.
\s UJesu uhamba phezu kolwandle
\p
\v 45 Njalo wahle wacindezela abafundi bakhe\x + Mat. 14.22-36. Joha. 6.15-21.\x* ukuthi bangene emkhunjini, njalo ba\add m\add*qalele ukuya ngaphetsheya\x + 6.32.\x* eBhethisayida\f + \fk eBhethisayida: \ft kumbe, \fq maqondana leBhethisayida\f*\x + Mat. 11.21.\x*, yena esayekela ixuku lihamba.
\v 46 Esebavalelisile, wasuka waya entabeni\x + Luka 9.61.\x* ukuyakhuleka\x + Mat. 14.23.\x*.
\v 47 Sekuhlwile, umkhumbi wawuphakathi kolwandle, futhi yena wayeyedwa emhlabathini.
\v 48 Wababona behlupheka kakhulu ekugwedleni, ngoba umoya wawuphambene labo, wasesiza kubo sokungaba yisikhathi somlindo wesine wobusuku, ehamba phezu kolwandle; wasefuna ukubadlula\x + Gen. 32.26. Luka 24.28.\x*.
\v 49 Sebembonile ehamba phezu kolwandle, basebecabanga ukuthi lithonga, bakhala kakhulu;
\v 50 ngoba bambona bonke, bethuka. Kodwa wahle wakhuluma labo, wathi kubo: Manini isibindi; yimi, lingesabi.
\v 51 Wasesenyukela kubo emkhunjini, umoya wasuthula; basebesanganiseka kakhulu okwedlula amalawulo ngaphakathi, bamangala\x + 7.37; 10.26.\x*.
\v 52 Ngoba babengaqedisisanga ngezinkwa\x + 8.17,18,21.\x*; ngoba inhliziyo yabo yayilukhuni\x + 3.5. 8.17. Joha. 12.40. Roma 11.7. 2 Kor. 3.14.\x*.
\s UJesu usilisa elizweni leGenesaretha
\p
\v 53 Kwathi sebechaphile bafika elizweni leGenesaretha, babophela umkhumbi ekhunjini.
\v 54 Bathi sebephumile emkhunjini, bahle bamazi,
\v 55 njalo bagijimela kuso sonke lesosigaba esizingelezeleyo, baqala ukubhoda bethwala abagulayo ngamathala bebasa lapho abebesizwa ukuthi ukhona.
\v 56 Njalo loba ngaphi angena khona emizaneni loba emizini, loba emaphandleni, babeka abagulayo emidangeni, bamncenga ukuthi bathinte umphetho wesembatho sakhe nje; njalo bonke abamthintayo basindiswa.
